WEBVTT

00:00.547 --> 00:03.444
- Previously on Gotham...
- It's you. It's really you.

00:05.928 --> 00:08.795
Oh, no. Somebody help!

00:08.831 --> 00:10.063
Penguin.

00:10.099 --> 00:11.665
He killed the librarian.

00:11.700 --> 00:15.068
I don't want to kill him.
I want to destroy him.

00:15.104 --> 00:16.637
And you promised them Jerome.

00:16.672 --> 00:18.772
They want to see his face.

00:18.807 --> 00:20.741
Behold the Prophet!

00:20.776 --> 00:22.142
We are Jerome!

00:22.178 --> 00:23.243
You get the message?

00:23.312 --> 00:24.611
We don't work for you no more.

00:24.647 --> 00:26.113
I will gut you!

00:26.148 --> 00:28.982
- Then Nygma dies.
- They have Ed.

00:29.018 --> 00:30.784
When I was last, you know, alive,

00:30.819 --> 00:31.852
I was about to kill Bruce Wayne.

00:31.887 --> 00:33.520
Well, where is my face?

00:33.556 --> 00:36.023
What?

00:36.058 --> 00:37.090
Oswald.

00:37.126 --> 00:38.692
- Where are you?
- Kane Chemicals.

00:38.727 --> 00:40.794
Oswald, hurry. Please?

00:40.829 --> 00:43.864
Tonight, Gotham, there are no rules.

00:43.899 --> 00:47.334
And when morning comes,
you, too, shall be...

00:47.369 --> 00:49.937
reborn.

00:49.972 --> 00:51.939
He's at the power
plant across the river.

